---
// About Section Component
---

<section id="about" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-24 md:mt-32 px-4 md:px-6 scroll-mt-24">
  <div
    class="border border-gray-700 bg-gray-800/60 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:border-cyan-400 transition duration-300 transform hover:scale-[1.01]"
  >
    <!-- Profile Section -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start gap-8 md:gap-12 p-6 md:p-10">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/images/profile.jpg"
            alt="Profile Photo"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-40 h-40 md:w-52 md:h-52 rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-cyan-400 shadow-2xl"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-cyan-400/20 to-blue-500/20"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 md:space-y-8 lg:pl-6 w-full">
        <!-- Main About Section -->
        <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500 mb-4">
              About Me
            </h2>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500 mx-auto lg:mx-0 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900/30 rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-gray-700/50">
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg mb-4 md:mb-6">
              I am a passionate Informatics Engineering student at Politeknik Negeri Malang with a deep fascination for full-stack development, 
              ranging from frontend user interfaces to backend systems and game development. My journey in technology began with curiosity 
              about how digital experiences are crafted, which has evolved into a comprehensive understanding of the entire development stack 
              and modern programming paradigms.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg mb-4 md:mb-6">
              Throughout my academic journey, I have developed a strong foundation in various programming languages and frameworks across 
              the full development spectrum. I thrive on solving complex problems through clean, efficient code, whether I'm crafting 
              intuitive user interfaces, building robust backend APIs, or creating immersive gaming experiences. My approach to development 
              emphasizes both technical excellence and user experience, ensuring that every project delivers meaningful value.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
              I am particularly drawn to the intersection of creativity and technology, where I can combine my technical skills across 
              frontend, backend, and game development to create comprehensive solutions. From responsive web applications to scalable 
              server architectures and interactive gaming experiences, I believe in continuous learning and staying updated with the 
              latest industry trends and best practices across all development domains.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Interests & Goals Grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-900/30 rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-gray-700/50 hover:border-cyan-400/50 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-heart text-cyan-400 text-lg"></i>
              <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">Interests & Hobbies</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
              Outside the world of coding, I enjoy playing various games across different genres, which not only provides entertainment but also 
              inspires my game development projects by understanding player psychology and engagement mechanics. I'm an avid anime enthusiast and 
              music lover, finding that these creative mediums often spark new ideas for my technical projects.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-900/30 rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-gray-700/50 hover:border-cyan-400/50 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket text-cyan-400 text-lg"></i>
              <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">Goals & Aspirations</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
              My long-term goal is to become a versatile full-stack developer who can contribute to innovative projects across all development 
              domains that make a positive impact on users' lives. I aspire to work on cutting-edge technologies spanning frontend interfaces, 
              backend systems, and gaming experiences that can handle complex real-world challenges. I'm always open to collaboration and eager 
              to contribute to open-source projects.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Fun Facts or Quick Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6">
          <div class="text-center p-4 md:p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 to-blue-500/10 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/20">
            <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400">2+</div>
            <div class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-400">Years Coding</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4 md:p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-pink-500/10 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/20">
            <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">10+</div>
            <div class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-400">Projects</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4 md:p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl border border-green-500/20">
            <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">5+</div>
            <div class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-400">Technologies</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4 md:p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/10 to-red-500/10 rounded-xl border border-orange-500/20">
            <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-orange-400">âˆž</div>
            <div class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-400">Passion</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </section>
